Hi, I am a Machine Learning Engineer with 3+ years of experience and my work revolves around defining Machine Learning problems, proposing innovative solutions and building research prototypes. I have developed end-to-end machine learning solutions and platform that runs not on servers but on smart devices demanding absolute precision in terms of accuracy and execution efficiency.
